headline: Two Utilities, Energy Stock Head To New Highs And Hover Near Buy Points
summary: Utility stocks are on a winning streak and some are at new highs on Friday.  Two of them — alongside an energy-sector issue — are near buy points and in buy zones in Friday's stock market.  National Fuel Gas is in a buy zone above a nine-weeks-long flat base with a buy point of 89.82.
